TRAILBLAZER:

        On the title screen hold down 'HELP', 'I', '1', and '2' then type
        "CHEAT".  During play use the following keys:

                'F3'__________________________Removes gravity.
                'F5'_______________________Changes ball shape.
                'F6'_______________Changes other players ball.
                'HELP'____________________________For a laugh.

